dc:description: Fake dog mummy, actually human child bones shaped like dog mummy
"Dog" mummy that contains a miscellaneous jumble of human child bones, possibly from more than one individual. Linen, pitch, human bones; 57.1 cm l., 16.5 cm w. (Death Dogs, Wilfong).
